Subject: drm/amdkfd: Replace zero-length array with flexible-array member
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: d5c831566d34924f62082f8b675d35c078f9b45c
